UR  - https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0304407694900329
KW  - Autoregressive moving average process
KW  - Exact ARMA covariance matrix
AB  - Several efficient methods to compute the exact ARMA covariance matrix are known. However, a general matrix representation in closed form is lacking. This article presents such a closed form. A matrix equation, containing the covariance matrix, is derived, and is solved for the MA, AR, and ARMA cases. The result is quite, and maybe surprisingly, simple.
